<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Password Reset - Eshop</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f6f8;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .container {
        background-color: #ffffff;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 40px auto;
        padding: 30px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #0070f3;
        color: white;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 24px;
        border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 20px;
        color: #333333;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.5;
      }
      .code-box {
        background-color: #f1f5ff;
        border: 1px dashed #0070f3;
        padding: 15px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: bold;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
        color: #1a202c;
        margin: 20px 0;
        border-radius: 8px;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 30px;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #888888;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .support-link {
        color: #0070f3;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">Password Reset Request</div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>Hello <strong><%= name %></strong>,</p>

        <p>
          We received a request to reset the password associated with your Eshop account.
          If you made this request, please use the code below to proceed:
        </p>

        <div class="code-box"><%= OTP %></div>

        <p>
          This code is valid for the next <strong>5 minutes</strong>. For your security,
          please do not share this code with anyone.
        </p>

        <p>
          If you did not request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email. Your account remains secure.
        </p>

        <div class="footer">
          Need help? Contact our support team at
          <a class="support-link" href="mailto:support@eshop.com"
            >support@eshop.com</a
          >.
          <br /><br />
          Â© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Eshop. All rights reserved.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
